/**
 * The `spec.IRefinementTypeProto` interface represents the specification of a refinement type.
 *
 * @name pentaho.type.spec.IRefinementTypeProto
 * @interface
 * @extends pentaho.type.spec.IValueTypeProto
 */

/**
 * The refinement facet ids or classes.
 *
 * The specified facet ids are added to the refinement type,
 * adding to any already present.
 *
 * The attributes defined by the added refinement facets become available for
 * extension/configuration on the refinement type.
 *
 * @name facets
 * @memberOf pentaho.type.spec.IRefinementTypeProto#
 * @type {Array.<string|Class.<pentaho.type.facets.Refinement>>}
 *
 * @see pentaho.type.Refinement.Type#facets
 */

/**
 * The representation type refined by this refinement type.
 *
 * Must and can only be specified at a top-refinement type, upon definition.
 *
 * @name of
 * @memberOf pentaho.type.spec.IRefinementTypeProto#
 * @type {!(pentaho.type.Element.Type|pentaho.type.List.Type)}
 *
 * @see pentaho.type.Refinement.Type#of
 */